    <body>
        <ul>
            <li>Close the Solstice app window.
            	<ul><li>On a laptop, click the Close 'X' icon. Solstice will ask if you wish to disconnect from the display and stop sharing all content. If yes, click <b>Disconnect</b>.</li><li>On a mobile device, close the app window and Solstice will automatically disconnect the device from the display.</li></ul></li>
            <li>With the Solstice app open and connected, click the <b>Disconnect</b> button at the top of the app window. You will be prompted to confirm that you want to disconnect from the display. </li>
        </ul>
    </body>
</html>